Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:52.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好...好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの...私でよかったら...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃...只要你不嫌弃我...
