Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,誰だ？そりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あ...あんたには  関係ないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,学...学长是谁 关你什么事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,関係ない  話をするな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不关我事那你还说个屁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,関係なくても！関係あるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是不关你事！但也关你事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,難しい話をするな！
Comment: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不要讲得这么复杂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你搁这跟爷讲绕口令呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:34.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ホワイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:34.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,White！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:35.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:35.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私達の目の前に  希望を...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,请将希望送到我们面前吧...！
